snippet.title: Astor: Blade of the Monolith – Official Release Date Trailer | tinyBuild Connect 2024
snippet.description:
⚔️ Astor: Blade of the Monolith is coming to PC and consoles on May 30th:
Strange events have set Astor on a quest for answers. In this fast-paced action RPG, use your newfound runic powers to battle through hordes of enemies. Find the ancient Monolith and use its secrets to save the planet from impending doom!

#IGN #Gaming
